{"tid":1457582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂]831係時候要黎翻一場和平大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T23:09:16.000Z","uid":45637,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eb26a22ec46c6c9cb218f6032f48d3369282ccea","tid":1457582,"uid":45637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"依個時候民怨最盛, 警又不停滲入玩分化打壓勇武<br />\n係時候重新集結翻所有人對準政權黎一次大集會<br />\n一黎前線手足可以抖抖<br />\n二黎警犬無辦法清場<br />\n三黎可以整頓一下士氣, 係主力軍翻學之前黎多次集會, 證明係好多人支持<br />\n重點係好多淺藍雖然唔想有衝突, 但其實對個政府都有好多不滿<br />\n所以唔好再比林鄭用警民衝突分散注意<br />\n五大訴求一定要逼到佢回應"},{"pid":"48d147dea57c5150df5acb441edeca2a7911a786","tid":1457582,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"好撚認真咁教你地做一次fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ff4f2792183187ffeca44bbdf93f6d574900a5d","tid":1457582,"uid":45637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"def678f1547a808594f33b002544247ab98501ec","tid":1457582,"uid":45637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"10dea5900b8ddebec7bcfd2038f577a673bc0ff5","tid":1457582,"uid":80232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"認真，係時候再一鼓作氣黎多鋪百萬人上街，今次一定會比二百萬更多"},{"pid":"ce17ef5ef78b09dfcf6ed236fb6c48284aff66ba","tid":1457582,"uid":4591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"818<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2407886579258719/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2407886579258719%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5%2F0N1eX%2FnGDFGLWAFE16zm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=efe8cb17\" data-auto-link targ